descriptionHtml: Delivering the ability to connect the Bryn Mawr Country Club to your mobile device. The Bryn Mawr Country Club app provides members with extraordinary functionality. Members can now view their monthly statements, book tee times, use the Club’s roster book to connect with other members, and even receive notifications of upcoming events. All of this functionality, and more, is available on your handheld or tablet mobile device.
